\+ performs checked addition, that normal addition (+),
except it throws a runtime exception on overflow.
To handle the variables as unsigned, use +\+

\- performs checked subtraction, that normal subtraction (-),
except it throws a runtime exception on overflow.
To handle the variables as unsigned, use +\-

\* performs checked multiplication, that normal multiplication (*),
except it throws a runtime exception on overflow.
To handle the variables as unsigned, use +\*

